<item>
            <title>[FELIX-3824] Possible InvalidStateException thrown while unregistering bundle services</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-3824</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I think there&apos;s a small possibility that an InvalidStateException is thrown when unregistering services after the bundle is stopped.  It can only happen if the registration is held by someone and unregistered concurrently with the bundle being stopped.&lt;br/&gt;
I think it does not hurt to catch and ignore it as I had it once.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
